␀␀␀␀#␀␀.␀␀6␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀N␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀A␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀8␀␀X␀␀m␀␀␀␀	␀␀␀␀L␀␀P␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀0␀␀o␀␀␀␀␀␀:␀␀>␀␀?␀␀e␀␀␀␀␀␀L␀␀P␀␀Q␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀?␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀p␀␀t␀␀4␀␀8␀␀= ␀␀A ␀␀B ␀␀l ␀␀p ␀␀n$␀␀r$␀␀x&␀␀|&␀␀}&␀␀&␀␀&␀␀'␀␀'␀␀'␀␀'␀␀(␀␀(␀␀?)␀␀H)␀␀5*␀␀9*␀␀␀,␀␀,␀␀/.␀␀3.␀␀C0␀␀G0␀␀1␀␀1␀␀74␀␀;4␀␀6␀␀6␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀:␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀9␀␀9␀␀␀ ␀!␀6␀␀q␀Richard OdermattC:\FILES\THFPAGE\BGUP263.DOCMildred H. GabronA:\BGUP263.HTMAnthony RosselloA:\BGUP263.HTM@HP LaserJet 4/4M␀LPT1:␀HPPCL5MS␀HP LaserJet 4/4M␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀g␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀	X␀␀X␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀@␀MSUDNHP LaserJet 4␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀;␀␀␀␀␀d␀
